net.hockeyapp.android.tasks

Class CheckUpdateTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<Void,String,org.json.JSONArray>
      • net.hockeyapp.android.tasks.CheckUpdateTask
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckUpdateTaskWithUI

    public class CheckUpdateTask
extends android.os.AsyncTask<Void,String,org.json.JSONArray>

    Description

    Internal helper class. Checks if a new update is available by fetching version data from Hockeyapp.
